Rating: 4
I make this all the time for myself, and when I make it for guests they seem to really like it to. My modifications: Omit orange juice and cinnamon, and definitely cut the ginger in half (to 1/8 cup). If you are going to add cream (or even the tiniest bit of butter), don't add it to the main batch, put a splash into each serving right before you serve it. This soup also happens to freeze really well so if you have a pot large enough it is really easy to double the batch.

